                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The cross section of monitor reaction equal 10.8-mb at",
                "the proton energy 1-GeV and 10-mb at more high energy."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
