            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " In the experiments were used six targets, three",
                "were directed fissioning side from proton beam, another",
                "three directed opposite side, fission fragments",
                "detected in range angle more 119-degree and less",
